description: Arnott’s Shapes Original Pizza are an Aussie favourite savoury biscuit snack with a rich flavour combination of tomato and melted cheese on a crispy,Arnott’s Shapes Originals are big on crunch and even bigger on taste – and perfect for any occasion! Whether you’re sharing with friends at the park or looking for a fun afternoon snack with flavours that your whole family will love, Arnott’s Shapes Original Pizza biscuits are the perfect flavoured cracker.
